{"tid":1952330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如個個月每一日都紀念日 每一日都出嚟送頭","createTime":"2020-03-31T14:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T17:30:53.000Z","uid":136967,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d069874a99a651e7a3eca601afddad94a289a589","tid":1952330,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"每一日都出黎搞一次<br />\n1號紀念10月1中槍學生<br />\n2號紀念罷課<br />\n3號紀念7區行街<br />\n4號紀念周梓樂<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n21號出嚟大搞 送一批頭<br />\n31號又送多批<br />\n<br />\n為搞而搞夠未？送夠頭未？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係咪唔搞就等於忘記？</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解咁難忘嘅事仲需要每個月出嚟提大家？</span></span></strong><br />\n個個出到嚟企 同班狗你眼望我眼 <br />\n等到最後一刻出嚟驅散走唔切先走<br />\n咁樣就光復到香港？咁樣受害嘅手足就有救？<br />\n要對得住班受害嘅手足原來係要一齊受害？<br />\n唔係話用念力光復香港 <br />\n但係有d野係咪唔好為做而做？"},{"pid":"64b368bea62bcd518a0aeee27915996729de400b","tid":1952330,"uid":267808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"而家仲要有4人法， worst timing"},{"pid":"1a0fe3c85d6c7c08799039a79cdda12489b7f888","tid":1952330,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"兒登仔係咁嫁啦<br />\n冇被捕冇警暴畫面=抗爭已完"},{"pid":"f235703d3c5c402dacfc511fdfbb77ece8c4acd7","tid":1952330,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b368bea62bcd518a0aeee27915996729de400b","tid":1952330,"uid":267808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"而家仲要有4人法， worst timing"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"今朝講唔排除即罰2000<br />\n夜晚即刻做<br />\n今晚大sir fatfat<br />\n仲有望住你地企都袋緊OT錢"},{"pid":"c5c4fc63f024f2ce1d04631adf632946cf7a718e","tid":1952330,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"其他人你控制唔到"},{"pid":"d150bf330f3c8f1758d4e4bc9ac3d9339e365946","tid":1952330,"uid":236003,"like":1,